{"tid":1752721,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"單票制 vs 比例代表制","createTime":"2019-11-24T23:14:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-24T23:16:36.000Z","uid":247607,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c6150041f26c6bf132c9680f975b1cf21d08f8f1","tid":1752721,"uid":247607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T23:14:36.000Z","msg":"咁樣的民情之下，得票率仍然係六四比<br />\n係區選單議席單票制之下，當然優勢盡見<br />\n下年立法會選舉去返比例代表制時，係配票高手操控之下，四成選票隨時可以取得當區一半議席，情況值得擔憂<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7v50L0J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7v50L0J.jpg&h=37be0a24&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"527a8315d1bb6eea454a2d98384718ed5d5805d9","tid":1752721,"uid":28938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T23:16:36.000Z","msg":"所以初選好重要，唔好再自己打自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}